data.description: This beauty has arrived in Sumter Co. You would not want to miss out on this home that sits beautifully on a spacious lot, front porch to sit your favorite rocking chair and drink coffee. This home has been freshly painted, new laminate flooring in the kitchen area and the carpet has been freshly shampooed. This home is move in ready and it has so much to offer. You can add your privacy fence of your choice around the yard at your own cost, build a outdoor kitchen in the back yard and so much more room to entertain friends and family. Call me today for a showing, becuase this home will not last long for this amazing listing price.
